   <div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">纪思翰（John S. Ji） 博士，副教授，博士生导师</span></b></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">主要学历</span></b></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-wrap: wrap;\">1. </span>2004-2008年&nbsp; &nbsp;约翰霍普金斯大学&nbsp; &nbsp;神经科学学士学位</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-wrap: wrap;\">2. </span>2008-2010年&nbsp; &nbsp;哈佛大学公共卫生学院&nbsp; &nbsp;流行病学硕士学位</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-wrap: wrap;\">3. </span>2010-2013年&nbsp; &nbsp;哈佛大学公共卫生学院&nbsp; &nbsp;环境健康博士学位</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">主要学术经历</span></b></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-wrap: wrap;\">1. </span>2017-2021年&nbsp; &nbsp;昆山杜克大学&nbsp; &nbsp;助理教授</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-wrap: wrap;\">2. </span>2021-2024年&nbsp; &nbsp;清华大学万科公共卫生与健康学院&nbsp; &nbsp;准聘副教授</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-wrap: wrap;\">3. </span>2025-至今&nbsp; &nbsp;清华大学万科公共卫生与健康学院&nbsp; &nbsp;长聘副教授</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-wrap: wrap;\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">其他学术经历</span></b></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 48px; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">1. 2017-2021年&nbsp; &nbsp;杜克大学尼古拉斯环境学院&nbsp; &nbsp;兼职助理教授</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">2. 2023-2024年&nbsp; &nbsp;约翰霍普金斯大学彭博公共卫生学院&nbsp; &nbsp;兼职副教授</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">3. 2024-至今&nbsp; &nbsp;华盛顿大学公共卫生学院&nbsp; &nbsp;附属副教授</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 48px; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">主要学术荣誉</span></b></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 48px; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-wrap: wrap;\">1. 2024年&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>自然科学基金委医学科学部优秀青年科学基金项目（优青）</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 48px; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"></span></b></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">学术期刊编辑</span></b></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 48px; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">202</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">-至今&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The BMJ《英国医学杂志》&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">副主编</span><br></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">2. 2016-2017年&nbsp; &nbsp;The Lancet《柳叶刀》&nbsp; &nbsp;高级编辑</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 48px; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">学术期刊编委</span></b></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 48px; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">1. 2024-至今&nbsp; &nbsp;《柳叶刀区域健康-西太平洋》&nbsp; &nbsp;国际咨询委员</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">2. 2024-至今&nbsp; &nbsp;《生物医学与环境科学》&nbsp; &nbsp;编委</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">3. 2025-至今&nbsp; &nbsp;《社会科学与医学》&nbsp; &nbsp;编委</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 48px; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">学术服务工作</span></b></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 48px; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">1. 世界卫生组织，气候健康伦理技术咨询组，联合组长</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">2. 国际环境流行病学学会，亚洲及西太平洋分会，常务委员</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">3. 中华预防医学会环境卫生分会，委员</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">4. 中国环境诱变剂学会环境流行病学专业委员会，委员</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">5. 中国环境诱变剂学会气候与健康专业委员会，委员</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">6. 中国环境科学学会环境医学与健康分会，委员</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">主讲教学</span></b></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-wrap: wrap;\">1.&nbsp;</span>公共卫生研究方法 </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-wrap: wrap;\">2.&nbsp;</span>队列研究设计：应用流行病学 </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-wrap: wrap;\">3.&nbsp;</span>星球健康</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">论文发表</span></b></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: symbol;font-size: 14px\">· </span><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">Xi D, Liu L, Zhang M, Huang C, Burkart KG, Ebi K, Zeng Y, Ji JS. Risk factors associated with heatwave mortality in Chinese adults over 65 years. </span><i><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">Nat Med.</span></i><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\"> 2024 May;30(5):1489-1498. doi: 10.1038/s41591-024-02880-4. Epub 2024 Mar 25. PMID: 38528168.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: symbol;font-size: 14px\">· </span><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">Song J, Liu L, Miao H, Xia Y, Li D, Yang J, Kan H, Zeng Y, Ji JS. Urban health advantage and penalty in aging populations: a comparative study across major megacities in China. </span><i><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">Lancet Reg Health West Pac.</span></i><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">2024 Jun 15;48:101112. doi: 10.1016/j.lanwpc.2024.101112. PMID: 38978965; PMCID: PMC11228801.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: symbol;font-size: 14px\">· </span><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">Ji JS, Xia Y, Liu L, Zhou W, Chen R, Dong G, Hu Q, Jiang J, Kan H, Li T, Li Y, Liu Q, Liu Y, Long Y, Lv Y, Ma J, Ma Y, Pelin K, Shi X, Tong S, Xie Y, Xu L, Yuan C, Zeng H, Zhao B, Zheng G, Liang W, Chan M, Huang C. China's public health initiatives for climate change adaptation. </span><i><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">Lancet Reg Health West Pac.</span></i><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\"> 2023 Nov 15;40:100965. doi: 10.1016/j.lanwpc.2023.100965. PMID: 38116500; PMCID: PMC10730322.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: symbol;font-size: 14px\">· </span><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">Qiu S, Chen X, Chen X, Luo G, Guo Y, Bian Z, Li L, Chen Z, Wu X, Ji JS. Solid fuel use, socioeconomic indicators and risk of cardiovascular diseases and all-cause mortality: a prospective cohort study in a rural area of Sichuan, China. </span><i><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">Int J Epidemiol.</span></i><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\"> 2022 May 9;51(2):501-513. doi: 10.1093/ije/dyab191. PMID: 34536011.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: symbol;font-size: 14px\">· </span><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">Ji JS, Zhu A, Lv Y, Shi X. Interaction between residential greenness and air pollution mortality: analysis of the Chinese Longitudinal Healthy Longevity Survey. </span><i><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">Lancet Planet Health.</span></i><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\"> 2020 Mar;4(3):e107-e115. doi: 10.1016/S2542-5196(20)30027-9. PMID: 32220672; PMCID: PMC7232951.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: symbol;font-size: 14px\">· </span><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">Ji JS, Zhu A, Bai C, Wu CD, Yan L, Tang S, Zeng Y, James P. Residential greenness and mortality in oldest-old women and men in China: a longitudinal cohort study. </span><i><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">Lancet Planet Health.</span></i><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\"> 2019 Jan;3(1):e17-e25. doi: 10.1016/S2542-5196(18)30264-X. PMID: 30654864; PMCID: PMC6358124.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: symbol;font-size: 14px\">· </span><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">Ji JS, Power MC, Sparrow D, Spiro A 3rd, Hu H, Louis ED, Weisskopf MG. Lead exposure and tremor among older men: the VA normative aging study. </span><i><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">Environ Health Perspect.</span></i><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\"> 2015 May;123(5):445-50. doi: 10.1289/ehp.1408535. Epub 2015 Jan 23. PMID: 25633720; PMCID: PMC4421770.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: symbol;font-size: 14px\">· </span><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">Ji JS, Elbaz A, Weisskopf MG. Association between blood lead and walking speed in the National Health and Nutrition Examination Survey (NHANES 1999-2002). </span><i><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">Environ Health Perspect.</span></i><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\"> 2013 Jun;121(6):711-6. doi: 10.1289/ehp.1205918. Epub 2013 Apr 19. PMID: 23603014; PMCID: PMC3672915.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: symbol;font-size: 14px\">· </span><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">Ji JS. Rainfall events and adverse health outcomes. </span><em><span style=\"font-family: 等线;\">BMJ.</span></em><span style=\"font-family: 等线;\">&nbsp;2024 Oct 9;387:q2053. doi: 10.1136/bmj.q2053. PMID: 39384299.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: symbol; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">· </span>Ji JS, Xi D, Huang C. Building resilience in heatwaves. </span><i><span style=\"font-family: 等线;\">Nat Med.</span></i><span style=\"font-family: 等线;\"> 2023 Jul;29(7):1613-1614. doi: 10.1038/s41591-023-02409-1. PMID: 37464046.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-family: 等线;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 10px; text-indent: 2em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-wrap: wrap;\">纪思翰（John S. Ji） 博士</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-wrap: wrap;\">副教授，博士生导师，国家优秀青年科学基金（优青）获得者</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-wrap: wrap;\">纪思翰博士于2008年毕业于美国约翰斯·霍普金斯大学，获得神经科学学士学位，随后于2010年和2013年在哈佛大学公共卫生学院分别获得流行病学硕士学位和环境健康科学博士学位。2017年至2021年，他在昆山杜克大学担任助理教授，并兼任国际环境政策硕士（iMEP）项目副主任。2021年至2024年，他在清华大学担任教研系列准聘副教授，2025年破格晋升为教研系列长聘副教授。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-wrap: wrap;\">纪思翰教授专注于气候变化与公共卫生的交叉研究，通过大规模队列研究量化环境健康风险，并探索人类韧性的作用机制。他的研究成果发表在《Nature Medicine》《The Lancet Planetary Health》等国际顶尖跨学科期刊，以及《International Journal of Epidemiology》和《Environmental Health Perspectives》等权威流行病学期刊。他牵头组织的《柳叶刀》西太平洋地区气候变化与健康适应专辑汇集了来自6个国家的101位学者。纪思翰连续多年入选斯坦福大学“全球前2%顶尖科学家”榜单。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-wrap: wrap;\">纪思翰现任《The BMJ》副主编，曾担任《The Lancet》高级编辑，并兼任《The Lancet Regional Health – Western Pacific》《Biostatistics &amp; Epidemiology》《Biomedical and Environmental Sciences》和《Social Science &amp; Medicine》的编委。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-wrap: wrap;\">在政策影响方面，纪思翰是世界卫生组织（WHO）气候健康伦理技术咨询组成员，主持了WHO西太平洋地区可持续适老化城市与社区建设项目，并受邀为《国家气候变化健康适应行动方案（2024—2030年）》提供技术建议。他还曾担任世界银行顾问。在学术合作方面，纪思翰教授作为华盛顿大学附属兼职教授，参与了全球疾病负担（GBD）研究。他是《柳叶刀》健康与气候变化倒计时中国报告的作者之一，负责城市绿色空间指标的研究工作。此外，他当选为国际环境流行病学学会（ISEE）亚太分会理事。近年来，他在第28届和第29届联合国气候变化大会（COP28和COP29）以及第77届和第78届世界卫生大会（WHA77和WHA78）期间组织边会，积极推动气候变化与健康议程的发展。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-wrap: wrap;\">在教学方面，纪思翰负责清华大学的多门核心课程和选修课程，包括《公共卫生研究方法 Public Health Research Methods》（必修）、《队列研究 Cohort Studies》（选修）以及新开设的《地球健康 Planetary Health》课程。</span></p>\n</div>\n                  </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"footer\">\n  <div class=\"wp flex zi3\">\n     <div class=\"logoft flex-v-center\">                <img src=\"../../images/logoft.svg\">\n</div>\n     <div class=\"infoft flex-v-center\">\n       <p class=\"link\">\n<a href=\"https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1855646458, 80887)\">清华大学主页</a>\n<a href=\"http://intranet.vsph.tsinghua.edu.cn\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1855646458, 80888)\">学院内联网（限内部用户）</a>\n</p>\n       <p class=\"copy\"></p><p>Copyright © 2020 清华大学万科公共卫生与健康学院 &nbsp;All Rights Reserved.</p><p></p>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"codeft\">\n            \t\t\t<img src=\"../../images/code.png\"><p>微信公众号</p>\n\n     </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"../../js/lib5.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"../../js/anime.min.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"../../js/particles.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"../../js/u.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"../../js/f.js\"></script>\n<!--<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/index.js\"></script>-->\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"../../js/public.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"../../js/ny_wow.js\"></script>\n\n\n</body></html>"
